 SSH is used to login from server1 to server2 without using Password 
 Password less conection is used to login from server1 to server2 without using .pem key or password 
 total no of arguments passed = $# 
 list of all arguments passwd = $*
 pid of the running process = $$ 
 pid of the lst command went into background = $!  
 to check the status of last executed command = $?
 script name = $0
 the arguments wil be stored in script in array format = $@
